title: Eagles get needed road win as goal-line woes plague Packers (Football 9/27)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to react to the Eagles win over the Packers on Thursday Night Football. The guys discuss Matt LaFleur's playcalling on the goal-line (5:00), an impressive road win for Philadelphia (22:00) and rant about pass interference and reviews in the NFL (29:30).
